{"word":"τέος 2","slug":"τέος 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n103089\" key=\"te/os2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τέος</orth> and <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τεός</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> and <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram> </gramGrp> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τίς, τις</foreign>, rare in nom. and acc., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔτε γὰρ οὔ τεον ἔστι</foreign> nor is there a No<sense id=\"n103089.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">thing</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1562.tlg001:8:46\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Parm.\">Parm.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.46</biblScope> </bibl>; but some of the oblique cases occur in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author></bibl>, etc., <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">τέῳ, τέων, τέοισι; τεοις</ref> </xr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0267.tlg001:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Xenoph.\">Xenoph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">37</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τέο</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}